ygData.messageBody:
I just gain the master in tinkering couple days ago and have since
made 10 aqualungs ... to skill of 105 now.

I just have 2 questions...
1)what prices are people selling these usually? (since people all
aruond me have told me that they would rather buy rebreather at a
later time instead of spending "any" pp on these..) I mean, I can
maybe support myself and train up my skills .. but this is getting
me down.
(600pp..including 500pp credit for a rebreather later..it's
like a loan yet no one's buying it...)

2)At what skill level should I start attempting on making rebreathers?

Maruk
Tinker Master of Bertoxxulous
